info.name: Ultimate Moonie Dashboard Icons
info.additionalInfo:
Your inbox icon will be the Crescent Moon Wand because it gives you the power to help answer questions.
Your "help?" will be Princess Usagi and Mamoru's Star Locket because get it, Mamochan didn't know who he was. HA.
Your settings will be the Luna Disguise Pen because you can customize your blog and such via the settings.
I do not have a icon for Missing E yet.
Your 'quit/logout' button with be the symbol for the Negamoon Family because Negatrash.
yep.
